				<td colspan="2"><span>I was kiting a swarm of undead amusing myself with the patterns of spell effects as you spin when I realized that there were a couple of casters standing on the hillside watching me. 
<br />
I ignored them at first .. then the chanter ran into the middle of the swarm and cast what lookedl ike an AE stun. Well .. I ran back a bit took a look at the situation wondering what was going on. 
<br />
I ask in /ooc What are you doing? 
<br />
They say.. your hogging all the mobs.  
<br />
/sigh I had maybe 15 on me at the most.
<br />
So I hit fading memories, if they want they can Have agro. 
<br />
Two screaming running casters flee towards the zone line, moments later I have my swarm back watching the pretty spell notes floating around us all as I spin in circles. 
<br />
Silly people should know better than to mess with a bard in mid kite, our agro is tentative at best if we're not consciously attempting to hold agro from others and viciously dangerous to anyone that shouldn't be involved. </span></td>
